flowchart TD
    User[User Browser] -->|HTTPS| ALB[Public Application Load Balancer]
    ALB --> Web[Presentation Tier]
    Web -->|Private traffic| AppALB[Internal Application Load Balancer]
    AppALB --> App[Application Tier: Hashing API]
    App -->|Retrieve pepper| Secrets[AWS Secrets Manager / SSM]
    App -->|Store hashes only| RDS[(RDS MySQL Private DB)]
    App --> Logs[CloudWatch Logs]
    CloudTrail[CloudTrail] --> S3[(Encrypted Audit Log Bucket)]
